Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:55.98,NOTES 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\shad0\bord0\c&H5C6062&\frz-7\move(820,304,814,294)}以待雷落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:06:00.52,NOTES 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\shad0\bord0\c&H5C6062&\frz-7\move(814,254,808,244)}若降落处有人 则有寄生于人脐
